column5: All,Anybody looking to go on a fly in to Northern Manitoba the week of 5-30 to 6-6? I need one guy. Awesome trophy pike fishing and great walleye fishing for size and numbers. Cost is about $2200.00 for one week all inclusive from winnepeg. If you are interested please e-mail me for the rest of the details. Thanks. Duffy
